I'm using LdapCredProvider for authentication but I still want to add users to the system.  If I specify ext. user management, I cannot add more users to the system.  I have to ext user mgmt off and then add users and then turn it back on again.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-3376].
  {panel}

It would be useful for the default POP3 Create Issue Handler to support more of the Issue fields via X-Headers.  For instance, it would be nice to be able to set the component(s) by adding "X-Component:" headers to the mail message, similar to the way that priority is handled already.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
